\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid224677 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 You know to theatres or to see a friend?
