No - only the - er - the only enjoyment was each year'd come round the Mothers Meetings had days out and she used to - she used to go on them, that's all. That was the only ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid224677 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 They were the only things she did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14629639 KW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 Yes. That was the only thing mum took an interest in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid224677 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 When did your father get home from work in the evenings. What time?
