Well - they - they would be the hard times. Mind you I always think they were good happy days - for all I had them hard - but - er - oh they were very, very hard - I know I'd gone 
to bed of a Sunday night crying and worrying where I was going to get the week's rent from and many a hungry tummy I've had. Believe me, my dad said to me when I was getting }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4926150 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
