 seven and once we heard that bell I'd have to look round for 'em and say come on, there's the bell and we'd have to run to be in for half past seven - for to get ready for bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid224677 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 So you would play with all the children in the neighbourhood would you?
