\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 'Don't you think I've got enough to do without washing the muck }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15687279\charrsid3944883 off}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 
