\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14629639 KW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 Well he never was ill until he died - but out of work it made a heck of a dif
ference - I was wondering whether where I was going to get the rent from.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid224677 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 And things were hard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14629639 KW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 Things were - well there was nothing you could do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid224677 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 He was out of work quite a lot was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14629639 KW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883 Oh yes. He was out - out of work ten solid months the first time I was - er - after I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4926150 
Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4986173\charrsid3944883  ten weeks. And then of course there was the - er the first world war broke out well then there was the big slump - he only got three days a week - so that was - er - that was it.

